<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-05-15T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-05-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="53" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d53">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Thompson</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Petropolis</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-05-15"><hi rend="italic">May 15,
                                1894</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>The Brazilian Government has recalled its minister at Lisbon and given
                            passports to the chargé d’affaires of Portugal.</p>
